description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Cooter purrs with a rating of 64, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 128, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 2 for East, 1 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90642-52192-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [128 Votes, Top 15% Score]
